text: Narowal is a city in Punjab, Pakistan. Narowal or Nurowal may refer to: *Narowal District, a district of Punjab (Pakistan) **Narowal Tehsil, a tehsil of district Narowal **Narowal Junction railway station, railway station in Pakistan *Nurowal, a village in India *Narawala, a village in Sri Lanka ==See also== * Narwal (disambiguation) * *
title: Narowal (disambiguation)
